{"tid":1913193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國每日電訊報盛讚蔡英文政府防疫工作做得好：為全球立下金牌標準","createTime":"2020-03-06T15:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T01:19:10.000Z","uid":28114,"like":109,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"7c01701b3c8b68b28c6e8e641733ea138f00d56b","tid":1913193,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:00:15.000Z","msg":"Taiwan sets gold standard on epidemic response to keep infection rates low<br />\n<br />\nEarly intervention, a clear command structure and transparent communication with the public have helped control the spread of the virus<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/content/dam/news/2020/03/05/TELEMMGLPICT000225235170_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqpVlberWd9EgFPZtcLiMQfyf2A9a6I9YchsjMeADBa08.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fnews%2F2020%2F03%2F05%2FTELEMMGLPICT000225235170_trans_NvBQzQNjv4BqpVlberWd9EgFPZtcLiMQfyf2A9a6I9YchsjMeADBa08.jpeg&h=2be5b89c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nA chemical unit of the Taiwanese army disinfects a quarantine compound<br />\n<br />\nTaiwan sits just 81 miles from the coast of China, more than 800,000 of its citizens live there and hundreds of daily connecting flights normally service business travel and tourism, but it has defied predictions of a widespread coronavirus outbreak and kept infection rates to just 44 isolated cases. <br />\n<br />\nAs nearby Japan and South Korea reel with thousands of infections, experts say Taiwan, an island of 23 million, has kept the virus at bay through early intervention, a slick command structure, well-rehearsed epidemic strategy and transparent communication that other countries including the UK could learn from. <br />\n<br />\nBy late December, before the coronavirus was on the world&rsquo;s radar, Taiwan&rsquo;s government was already sensing danger from rumours of a new respiratory disease emerging from Wuhan, and officials began boarding flights to check the health of passengers from the Chinese city....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/03/06/taiwan-sets-gold-standard-epidemic-response-keep-infection-rates/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2020%2F03%2F06%2Ftaiwan-sets-gold-standard-epidemic-response-keep-infection-rates%2F&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=564504e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2020/03/06/taiwan-sets-gold-standard-epidemic-response-keep-infection-rates/</a>"},{"pid":"7393ca5e29e7c10d2bfa7a568f8401352fe4586a","tid":1913193,"uid":31215,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"談得失出黎講兩句"},{"pid":"aba70702041f78f3143018152674430cbf7ffe8c","tid":1913193,"uid":37869,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"Taiwan no.1"},{"pid":"78cfcac42ccb31b98e2263bf25296174eebb4833","tid":1913193,"uid":289708,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:02:20.000Z","msg":"台灣對大陸封關果陣<br />\n大陸聲都唔敢聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688be5fb7338a90721f534bf13d5c53399a6fcc6","tid":1913193,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2d6feb4a89700e4eae2694bbf8392b16b7cc98","tid":1913193,"uid":85396,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T15:06:47.000Z","msg":"各國同台灣另起爐灶取代cho啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322eff813b00c395d791a24232fa485ede48d7a1","tid":1913193,"uid":28114,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"78cfcac42ccb31b98e2263bf25296174eebb4833","tid":1913193,"uid":289708,"like":47,"dislike":0,"s